sv.title: H e j
sv.text: Vad roligt att du har hittat hit! Vill du lära känna mig bättre eller ta del av min kreativitet? Då har du kommit helt rätt. Välkommen!

en.title: H e l l o
en.text: I’m glad you found your way here! Would you like to know me better or take part in my work and creativity? Then you have come to the right place. Welcome!

information.title: Ekbladet
information.subTitle: Established 1983
information.text: Student magazine belongs to the student association HHUS at Umeå University. Ekbladet has a circulation of 2,000 copies. As editor-in-chief in 2018, I was primarily responsible for the magazine's content, layout and communication both internally and externally. Feel free to see the newspapers online!
